@startuml
title Verification Separation

skinparam backgroundColor #F7F1E6
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam dpi 135
skinparam defaultFontName Georgia
skinparam defaultFontSize 15
skinparam TitleFontSize 20
skinparam NoteFontSize 14
skinparam ArrowFontSize 13
skinparam ArrowColor #5E5A53
skinparam PackageBorderColor #1D1D1D
skinparam PackageFontColor #161616
skinparam RectangleBorderColor #1D1D1D
skinparam RectangleBackgroundColor #F2E9D9
skinparam RectangleFontColor #161616
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #F5EBDD
skinparam NoteBorderColor #8C2721
skinparam NoteFontColor #7B1E1E
skinparam TitleFontColor #161616
skinparam RectangleRoundCorner 10

top to bottom direction

rectangle "Coordinator" as coord #E8DDD0
rectangle "Implementation Worker" as impl #EFE6D8
rectangle "Verification Worker" as verify #EFE6D8
rectangle "Runtime / Hooks /\nTask System" as runtime #EFE6D8

coord --> impl
impl --> runtime
runtime --> coord
coord --> verify
verify --> runtime
runtime --> coord

impl -[hidden]down- runtime
coord -[hidden]down- verify

note right of impl
implementation task
end note

note left of runtime
code changes + self-check
end note

note left of verify
independent verification
end note

note right of runtime
proof / failure / edge cases
verification result
end note

note bottom of verify
verification 必须与 implementation
分离。否则系统会把
“我改完了”
误当成
“它已经正确了”。
end note

@enduml
